Sentencas: In this study, nickel based woven meshes are tested as not only anode current collecting meshes but also anode flow fields instead of the conventional gas channels fabricated by machining.
Titulo: Design and fabrication of novel anode flow-field for commercial size solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: For this purpose, short stacks with different anode flow fields are designed and built by using different number of meshes with various wire diameters and widths of opening.
Titulo: Design and fabrication of novel anode flow-field for commercial size solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A short stack with classical machined flow channels is also constructed.
Titulo: Design and fabrication of novel anode flow-field for commercial size solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Performance and impedance measurements of the short stacks with commercial size cells of 81 cm(2) active area are performed and compared.
Titulo: Design and fabrication of novel anode flow-field for commercial size solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The results reveal that it is possible to create solid oxide fuel cell anode flow fields with woven meshes and obtain acceptable power with a proper selection of the mesh number, type and orientation.
Titulo: Design and fabrication of novel anode flow-field for commercial size solid oxide fuel cells
